      <title>卢旺达总统有望以 99% 的得票率获得第四个任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/rwanda-s-president-is-set-to-secure-fourth-term-with-99-of-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢旺达总统保罗·卡加梅在已统计的五分之四选票中赢得 99% 的选票，获得又一个五年任期，延续其对这个东非国家二十五年的统治。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/rwanda-s-president-is-set-to-secure-fourth-term-with-99-of-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:55:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜驻古巴高级外交官叛逃至韩国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/senior-north-korean-diplomat-based-in-cuba-defects-to-the-south</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜驻古巴的一名高级外交官于 11 月叛逃韩国，成为近年来离开这个封闭国家前往韩国的最高级别外交官之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/senior-north-korean-diplomat-based-in-cuba-defects-to-the-south</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 04:03:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟国家考虑重新开放阿富汗大使馆并承认塔利班</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/eu-nations-mull-reopening-afghan-embassies-recognizing-taliban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，几个欧洲国家正考虑重新开放其驻阿富汗大使馆，此举将意味着在喀布尔沦陷近三年后对塔利班的外交承认。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/eu-nations-mull-reopening-afghan-embassies-recognizing-taliban</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国经济学家怀疑工党政府促进经济增长的能力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/uk-economy-outlook-analysts-doubt-labour-can-boost-gdp-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项调查显示，英国经济学家对基尔·斯塔默领导的工党政府促进经济增长的能力表示怀疑，他们预计过去十年大部分时间困扰英国经济的缓慢扩张局面仍将持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/uk-economy-outlook-analysts-doubt-labour-can-boost-gdp-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国准备组建看守政府，但具体职责尚不明确</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/france-readies-for-caretaker-government-with-exact-remit-unclear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙即将启动看守政府的任命程序，直至寻找新总理的谈判取得成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/france-readies-for-caretaker-government-with-exact-remit-unclear</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩妹妹警告韩国将为散发传单付出“惨痛代价”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/kim-jong-un-s-sister-warns-south-korea-it-will-pay-gruesome-price-for-leaflets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩的妹妹警告首尔，越过边境散发反平壤传单将让其付出“惨痛”的代价，这表明朝鲜在向韩国发放装满垃圾的气球后可能会加大赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/kim-jong-un-s-sister-warns-south-korea-it-will-pay-gruesome-price-for-leaflets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 03:07:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普副总统候选人万斯称中国是美国“最大威胁”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/trump-s-vp-pick-vance-says-china-is-the-biggest-threat-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自被任命为唐纳德·特朗普的竞选搭档以来，JD 万斯在首次接受采访时将中国称为美国面临的最大威胁，并强调一旦当选，美国政府可能会对北京采取强硬立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/trump-s-vp-pick-vance-says-china-is-the-biggest-threat-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 03:06:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>情报机构证实朝鲜驻古巴外交官 11 月叛逃韩国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-16/urgent-north-korean-diplomat-in-cuba-defected-to-south-korea-in-november-seoul-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，韩国（美联社）——韩国情报机构周二称，朝鲜驻古巴的一名高级外交官已逃往韩国，这是近年来朝鲜统治精英成员一系列叛逃事件中的最新一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-16/urgent-north-korean-diplomat-in-cuba-defected-to-south-korea-in-november-seoul-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:22:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟委员将缺席匈牙利会议讨论奥尔班外交问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/eu-commissioners-to-skip-hungary-s-meetings-over-orban-diplomacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为抗议欧盟总理维克托·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）对莫斯科和北京的外交访问，欧盟委员会将减少参加欧盟轮值主席国匈牙利计划举行的非正式会议的级别。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/eu-commissioners-to-skip-hungary-s-meetings-over-orban-diplomacy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:44:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谈判进展不明朗，肯尼亚准备迎接更多抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/kenya-braces-for-more-protests-with-crisis-talks-status-unclear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托提出的帮助结束该国政治危机的谈判似乎陷入停滞，肯尼亚准备迎接更多的反政府抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/kenya-braces-for-more-protests-with-crisis-talks-status-unclear</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 12:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
